      <desc>The ship&apos;s view screen is filled with the image of a water covered world with one single island.  Upon the island is built a single tower that rises out of the water and stretches towards the heavens.  Your ship receives a tight beam transmission from Purgatorio Ground Control, &quot;Greetings Traveler.  Purgatorio is not yet opened, but please visit at a later date.&quot;</desc>
