   <location num='329' flags='sl'>
      <name>La Comedia Link</name>
      <desc>You have entered the passage to the afterlife.  The swirls of gaseous nebulae abound and provide a sureal view of the system.  The Comedia system is so named because it mirrors the divine comedy of life and the rewards and punishments that await departed souls.  Through the ship&apos;s view screen, beyond the swirling gasses, a trio of planets, in a horizontal line can be seen to the north.  The center planet appears to be covered in water.  Beneath it is a fiery, dark world, it&apos;s smoldering embers visible even from this distance.  The upper planet is shrouded in a soft mist, and it&apos;s green landscape peers through the mist which creates the appearance of a halo.</desc>
      <exits n='265' no-exit='moves.noexit.1'/>
   </location>

   <location num='526' flags='s'>
